    <p class="review_top-text review_margin-top">Pepperstone started from Australia and now is operating in 65 different countries and it received the nomination of the best ECN broker in Asia by forex.com.cn. It was also among BRW Fast Starters' top 100 fastest growing companies in Australia and was declared #1 rising Star by Deloitte as well. Pepperstone has earned a global reputation through its high quality of service, second to none trading platform and stellar customer support.</p>
